name: New Firecraker Aqua Blue and Cherry Red Timeless Twine
Timeless Twine Bakers Twine - 160 Yard Spools
description:
Go from Ordinary to EXTRAORDINARY! 

Timeless Twine takes pride in offering this eco-friendly twine. It's made from 100% cotton, bio-degradable and has a strong 4-ply construction. Timeless Twine is made in the USA !!!


You will receive:

{160 Yards} in the color of your choice (1 Spool)

** Please Note:  Halloween and Christmas Timeless Twine are sold out.

The perfect compliment to any package - simply wrap bakers twine around it for a beautiful finish. Baker's twine can be used to embellish gifts, baked goods, treat boxes, favor bags, tags, cards, scrapbooking projects and much more! 


***When purchasing Timeless Twine™ you agree to label product as Timeless Twine and not re-brand or un-brand Timeless Twine as your own or another brand.


*Please note* Timeless Twine has not been tested for direct food contact and is for decorative purposes only.
